    • 构造器详细资料

      • GroupClient

        public GroupClient(String appkey,
           String masterSecret)
        Create a Group Client with default parameters.
        参数:
        appkey - The key of one application on JPush.
        masterSecret - API access secret of the appKey.

      • GroupClient

        public GroupClient(String appkey,
           String masterSecret,
           cn.jpush.api.common.connection.HttpProxy proxy)
        Create a Group Client with a proxy.
        参数:
        appkey - The key of one application on JPush.
        masterSecret - API access secret of the appKey.
        proxy - The proxy, if there is no proxy, should be null.

      • GroupClient

        public GroupClient(String appkey,
           String masterSecret,
           cn.jpush.api.common.connection.HttpProxy proxy,
           JMessageConfig config)
        Create a Group Client by custom config. If you are using JMessage privacy cloud or custom parameters, maybe this constructor is what you needed.
        参数:
        appkey - The key of one application on JPush.
        masterSecret - API access secret of the appKey.
        proxy - The proxy, if there is no proxy, should be null.
        config - The client configuration. Can use JMessageConfig.getInstance() as default.
